data.description: Welcome home to the community of Horizon Park! This two story home has a two car garage and five bedrooms with a loft. It is a multigenerational design with a bedroom and full bathroom downstairs! Plenty of space in the kitchen and an open floor plan with a large dining room. Upstairs is a second living are/ loft with a laundry room. The master bedroom is a large size with a full master bathroom including double sinks and a separate tub/shower and walk in closet. And 3 more bedrooms and a full guest bathroom.
